      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, formal iterative convergence monitoring is sufficient; detailed round-off or floating-point error analysis is not required.",
      "rationale": "Iterative convergence was monitored via residual norms (below 1e-5 for all equations) and stabilization of the hemolysis index QoI. Formal numerical solver error quantification beyond convergence monitoring is not required at MRL 2 and was not performed."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
