      "rationale": "The simulation plan was documented and reviewed by a senior CFD analyst prior to execution. Formal use-error assessment including independent re-execution or double-blind analysis is not required at MRL 2 and was not performed."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, model form selection must be documented with engineering justification; formal model form uncertainty quantification is not required.",
      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model was selected based on published literature for rotating machinery hemolysis prediction. The power-law hemolysis damage model (Giersiepen et al.) is the accepted standard for this application. Formal model form UQ is not required at MRL 2."
    },
