    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. Output comparison exceeds the required level (achieved level 3 vs required level 2), providing additional confidence. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Note: this package conforms to ProfileMinimal; the digital signature is pending completion of the institutional signature workflow and will be affixed in a subsequent revision.",
